Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃 旦那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:13.16,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}字：给梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于成为岛内住民的梅梅与河童远野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后决定就住在我家附近的水车屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 梅梅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去田里要野菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野也一起去了 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只乌龟顶用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说了 远野是河童啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人叫我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啊 尤里你错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 听到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:00:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:47.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改变 梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我记得你是新人梅梅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这奇怪装束的是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 那个 请请请给我一点野菜...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:02:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难为情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起 这里就是梅梅的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么需要的 等会儿再去别人家问问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有点吵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是感动得说不出话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前露宿比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你漂到岛上后一直是在北森生活的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我很害羞 总是在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是那个有两只尾巴的老虎先生 特别可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这里简直就是天国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对远野来说 也是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童需要水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了那不是河童是乌龟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人你真顽固...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是顽固这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是甲壳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅怎么会跟远野一起旅行的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个听者伤心闻者落泪的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又演纸戏...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像在哪儿见过...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.59,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KUSO东映的LOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天老爸我做了咖喱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 老爸真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最爱你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能...交到一百个朋友吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像之前所说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了克服害羞的缺点而旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在某一天...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实远野 以前做了坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封印在了某个河边的小庙里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看它很可怜 就费心思将封印解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是以前充满回忆的小河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已不能再供河童居住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起去找美丽的河和同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫 梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此这般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟还恩...浦岛太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后梅梅就是龙宫城的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游下去抓不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅 砧板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多一点盘子就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么需要的 等会儿再去别人家问问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 总不能老给他们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 至少能减少一点羞耻度...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要自己一个去跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以带上了面具？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能老依靠行人和铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么说...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想像到与人相遇的场景...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放不下心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个以前遇到过的人 应该能稍微轻松点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也 也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是玲玲的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岛上唯一的匠人家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们从做掏耳勺到建家一切包办哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们帮我和远野修好家的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去好好道谢才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:09:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚂蚁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五 六 七 八 九 十
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「蚂蚁十只」...「谢谢」？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说你帮她修好水车屋的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 不用在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了我做的衣柜怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很...很容易打开 很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懂说话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴 我第一次被人夸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人都说我的作品是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的锅和盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都当附赠品送给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好...万分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然算是把想要的拿回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这些能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习...习惯了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她那么高兴 也无法拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅 这是个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...雪乃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是熊 和我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不是熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要穿玩偶装？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较容易接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才难以接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那实在太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃和企企都快被吓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是千影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是行人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心 千影是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的中国服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面超短 后面长裙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是岛外的最新时尚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影 STO～～～～P
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上新住民？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个让我背黑锅的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没跟我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去找犯人而躺在这里睡午觉的又是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想起来就火大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个叫梅梅的 从岛外来的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像成了行人殿下的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个怎样的新人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也比不上我一个脚指头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有什么重要的事情...忘记跟绫音...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是梅梅...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个新人倒挺嚣张的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影平常是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到岛外的东西性格就会转变是她的小小缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在扼杀于摇篮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来我还是没和任何人好好交流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要慢慢努力就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿真的呆得下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好讨厌这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我好想改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅被人看到就会害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要变装啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是新人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不会再偷东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷东西？你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估计是把绫音当成麻知姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫绫音 是追赶梅梅那人的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我和那没教养的姐姐不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被称为岛上最美丽最贤淑之美少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散布这谣言的是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是绫音的妄想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的两人 你们很失礼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才听到你们的说话了 你真是可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音你就从没想到改变自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个愚蠢的问题 行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算做事犯错 被鄙视
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还是会觉得自己可爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 今天的晚饭是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我还没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 现在你最应该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是改变自己害羞的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是喜欢上自己吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己...喜欢上我自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我有能让自己喜欢上的优点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才刚见面怎么可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能正如绫音所说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的梅梅也有优点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能独自旅行的胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画画又画得好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还为俺找同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也找到了你的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:17:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢你这搞笑的害羞样子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只要喜欢上自己恢复自信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞的个性也会改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上有过这种动物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是与梅梅一同漂流到这岛上的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟会叫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟会吃黄瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 它是河童啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 它是河童远野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说了世上没河童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人你就是死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河...河童？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌～～我讨厌河童～～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 好像绫音以前被河童袭击过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道俺的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉俺 告诉俺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉俺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你别过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音 没路了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音 梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下...永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音 快回来 绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有河童的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 远野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童就在这儿咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我为了吓绫音变装的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为绫音吃惊的样子很有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童...河童...河童...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 全是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就做了中国服 想请你们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅 这才是真正的熊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只才奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起跑来搭话 梅梅会被吓到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都为了我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅是这里的住民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后有事尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
